  "overview": {
    "title": "Infallible",
    "description": "Meta-achievement (ID 9106): \"Complete all Down and Out achievements\" — one per raid wing, 8 total. Grants the Infallible title. Considered the hardest raid achievement in GW2.",
    "rules": [
      "Fully clear the wing within the time limit, starting at the wing's trigger point (official in-game rule)",
      "No one in the squad may be DOWNED during the entire wing (official in-game rule)",
      "If a boss has a Challenge Mode, the CM must be enabled to earn credit (official in-game rule, W3-W8)",
      "W8: Ura must be done in LEGENDARY mode (official in-game rule)",
      "Cannot be done with Emboldened enabled (official in-game rule)"
    ],
    "source": "Official GW2 API (/v2/achievements). Time limit values are not published in game data; numbers below are community-documented (Snow Crows, Mar 2026) and pending our own in-game verification."
